Package realtimeweb.businesssearch.regular

Interface Summary
BusinessDataListener A listener for handling data received about a specific Business.
BusinessSearchListener A listener for handling data received about a list of businesses.
 

Class Summary
Business A Business object represents a Business in the real world.
BusinessSearch The StructuredBusinessSearch class is used to connect to the Yelp service and retrieve data as well-structured classes.
Deal A Deal is an offer made by the Business, such as a "2-for-1 Sale".
DealOption A DealOption is an item in a Deal.
DetailedLocation A location that contains highly detailed information, including both the latitude/longitude coordinates and address.
GiftCertificate A GiftCertificate is something you can buy to give as a present to someone else, and will have the value of however much you bought.
GiftCertificateOption An option for a Gift Certificate - that is, a possible value for a gift certificate to have (for instance, Kohl's might have $10, $20, and $50 gift cards available).
Review A Review contains user-supplied information about a Business.
SearchResponse A SearchResponse is returned by a search of businesses around a Location.
User A User is someone who uses the Yelp service.
